casebody.data:
James W. RILEY, petitioner,
v.
DELAWARE. No. 13-9254. Supreme Court of the United States April 28, 2014. Case below, 83 A.3d 738 . Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Delaware dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
